              %h4 What the fock is Grok?
              %p <em>Greenville Grok</em> — a small thing, in a great place with wonderful ideas producing an utterly profound experience. Grok is a teaching &amp; learning thing, for everyone.
            .span5
              %h4 Grok is 100% free.
              %p And always will be. It's a core belief that helps keep this conference small and real. We won't grow into a behemoth conference; it would kill the awesome.

