            %p All tickets are free and are available, one per person, at <a href="http://www.eventbrite.com/event/2722084829/eorg">EventBrite</a> on January 18th at 12pm for locals &mdash; anybody currently residing in South Carolina, Georgia, North Carolina, or Tennesee. Then for all y'all that live outside of God's country, we'll let you in on January 19th at 12pm. A total of 100 tickets are available.

